rComments: Prof. Kaplan's got a lot of enthusiasm which makes material about vague art & culture theory a lot *easier* to get into, if not *easy*. He's got a loud voice, clear facts, but doesn't spell it out for you. Open with students and willing also to open the room up to questions; if no one asks, he puts queries himself. Having him as a prof is a treat!
Very knowledgeable professor, very informative and very helpful! A great prof!
